 Mandriva Linux Security Advisory                         MDVSA-2014:120
 http://www.mandriva.com/en/support/security/
 _______________________________________________________________________

 Package : miniupnpc
 Date    : June 10, 2014
 Affected: Business Server 1.0
 _______________________________________________________________________

 Problem Description:

 Updated miniupnpc packages fix security vulnerability:
 
 The miniupnpc library before 1.9 may be vulnerable to a denial of
 service due to a buffer overrun that can be triggered by something
 on the network.
 _______________________________________________________________________

 References:

 http://advisories.mageia.org/MGASA-2014-0224.html
 _______________________________________________________________________

